Product name: ANTIQUE GERMAN Joseph's Coat Handmade large Marble
Description:
ANTIQUE GERMAN Josephs Coat Handmade large Marble
Blue, Turquoise, white
 1 1/2 " Handmade Marble Shooter 
A large antique Shooter size  marble
with Pontil and manufacturing marks and chips/flea bites
The earliest glass marbles were generally made by creating long canes that would have a clear or transparent-colored base surrounding tiny rods of colored glass. The molten blob would be pulled to create a slender cane that might be 20 to 50 feet long. The cane would be heated until it was maleable enough to be twisted and cut at one end with marble scissors, which were created around 1846 and had a little cup on them that would help form the hot glass into a perfect sphere.
I believe this is a marble by Kuhnert & Company (Company founded by Gunter Kuhnert and his sons In 1861 ) Please see middle marble on second row of final image.

Product name: Antique French Mirror - Antique French Louis XVI Period Gilt Mirror with Antique Glass
Description:
Antique French Mirror - Antique French Louis XVI Period Gilt Mirror with Antique Glass
This is a wonderful French mirror featuring a simple gilt frame around the glass. 
The frame itself is a traditional moulded frame on the outside edge and has the  gilt beading on the inside next to the glass. The frame has a lot of charm and wear with the worn layers of gilt work.
In the 18th century they would make the main frame and then apply it on another frame (behind it). If you look from the side you see the second frame, which gives it authenticity and a wonderful look.  
The back of the mirror is antique wood but does not look to be original.  We believe the glass was replaced at some point with old antique glass.
The mirror itself appears to be old Mercury glass, which is glass that was originally produced in the 19th century.  The glass has the appearance of looking hazing and has some missing silver. This makes this mirror exceptionally charming, because of the distressed glass. 
This mirror is currently set up for a "portrait" handing with basic eye hooks and wire. It can easily be changed to hang sideways or "landscape" for the look of your choice.
Circa 1790
Imported directly from France
Condition:
Rough Antique Condition
Well worn frame and highly distressed glass
Measurements
25.25" x 19.25" x 1.75"

Product name: Lithograph Ludwig van Beethoven by Max Wulff 1912
Description:
Extremely rare lithograph of Ludwig van Beethoven, by Max Wulff from 1912. Size: 49 x 40 cm. The picture is framed and was given as a gift in 1933. The text says "Christmas 1933. From mother!". The lithograph is in very good condition without water marks or discoloring. 
The lithograph is mentioned in the Beethoven-library, Bonn Germany: 
http://www.beethoven-haus-bonn.de/sixcms/detail.php?id=&template=opac_bibliothek_en&_opac=bild_en.pl&_dokid=bi:xx:142431281
On their litho there is a text in the center of the litograph saying "Beethoven". This text has been cut off the one for sale here and glued on the back of the frame, probably to make it fit the frame (see photo of the back). 
Further photos can be emailed on request.

10 - Mint to near mint condition with minimum to minor signs of handling.

Product name: 100% Natural Paw Balm for dogs - Paw Wax
Description:
Protect your pampered pet's paws from the elements with this Paw Balm.  
We start with coconut oil, infused with organic calendula flowers, beeswax for it's protective qualities and a touch of neem oil.  Beeswax will act as a protective coating against snow and salt, while oils moisturize.  
For small dogs, place their warm paw on top of the balm and rotate the tin to apply.  You may want to work in with your hands.  For bigger dogs, you can use the same method, just doing parts of the paw at a time.  Or simply scoop a little product out with a popsicle stick or the back of your fingernail and rub it into their paw pads.  
Great for pets who don't mind going out for walks in the cold and snow.  Our Jack Russell Terrier, Maggie, is more of a do your business and get back in the house warm weather lover, but we still use to moisturize and protect her paws for those couple minutes outside at a time!
2 oz tin

This is a bag of our top choice moss. It is guaranteed pesticide free and pre-cleaned. It is a hand selected blend of 10 species of mosses and lichens. Product name: Invitro Fertility (IVF) Planner Stickers for Erin Condren, Plum Paper, Filofax, Kikki K, Limelife, Inkwell Press, Happy Planner, & Planners
Description:
Preparing for an IVF procedure or are you starting from the beginning of this course of fertility treatment? Mark your progress and important procedures with these stickers.
Included are over 180 stickers including Cycle Start, Egg Retrieval, Med Change (8), Embryo Transfer (2), Beta Check (8), Bed Rest (4), Doctor Appointment (7), Ultrasound (4), POAS (3), Follicle Count (5), 90 pill stickers and 72 injection stickers for any related medication you might need to mark. The stickers are no wider than 1.4".
These stickers come on 2 (two) 7.5 x 5.875 sheets with a punch guide to place the sheet in a mini binder.
As a surrogate, I've seen first hand how devastating infertility can be. That is why I decided to come up with several sets to help those involved within the IUI, IVF and other processes to make their steps in their individual journeys. I wish you all the sticky thoughts and baby dust your way to make your dreams of a family come true!
I started with an empty planner and coloring pencils. I drew various images into my planner before moving up to drawing on sticker paper and cutting them out. Once I discovered planner stickers the sky was the limit for me. I used them to mark important dates and times and then for fun and decoration!
These stickers are printed on matte sticker paper, making it easy to write on them with any type of pen or marker you prefer. You can use them as-is, as a regular sticker, or to take down notes, to-do lists, reminders, appointments, etc.! The size, height, width, etc. of each sticker varies depending on the particular image. These stickers are perfect for adding some colorful flair and POP to your planner whilee also making important items, dates, appointments, and more stand out on your page!
All stickers come on sheets and individually die-cut, ready to easily peel off and stick onto your planner, calendar, note cards, gifts, decorations, or scrapbook projects! Please look at the included photos for a reference to their size in the Erin Condren Life Planner daily box in the weekly view. Your stickers will be professionally packaged and ready to use yourself or to give as a gift!
Glossy and matte vinyl stickers are available for any sticker for an additional charge. Glossy stickers are an additional 1 and matte vinyl stickers (which are made out of a water resistant vinyl material) are an additional 1.75 per set.
If you want a combination of matte, glossy, or matte vinyl, leave a note in the “notes to seller” section indicating which sticker type you would like in which finish if you haven’t already done so.
All orders are printed and cut upon RECEIVING the order due to the large amount of personalization on orders received. If you have any questions or need a rush order, please message me and I will work with you to meet your needs.
I love making stickers. I am constantly working on new additions to my shop while processing and filling orders. I also work full time- sometimes up to 50 hours a week- while also running a busy household including a rambunctious infant! I list my processing time as 1-2 weeks and most of the time I beat that expected time. I work 5 days a week on my shop but I do take 2 days a week to spend with my family!
Thank you for looking at my shop and I look forward to sending you something that will help you organize your life!

Product name: Modern Calligraphy Worksheet - PRINTABLE DOWNLOAD - Slightly Fancy Alphabet Exemplar, Calligraphy Practice Sheets, Letter Formation
Description:
Download and print this fun practice worksheet and up your modern calligraphy game!
This worksheet contains a full alphabet exemplar (upper case and lower case) with numbered strokes so you can learn exactly how to form each letter. Then, you get 10 pages of worksheets so you can practice tracing and then writing each letter. Finally, you'll practice combining the letters by writing some common (and not so common) words.  
This is a DOWNLOADABLE PDF - you will not receive anything physical in the mail! Instead, you will receive a link in your Etsy invoice, so you can can instantly download and print out this worksheet at home. 
This is a WORKSHEET ONLY and does not come with any calligraphy tools. For an introduction to modern calligraphy tools and techniques, download my comprehensive introductory GUIDEBOOK here:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/489632076/modern-calligraphy-guidebook-printable?ref=shop_home_feat_3
------------------------
WORKSHEET CONTENTS:
This 14-page worksheet is an original written work by Shinah of Crooked Calligraphy, full of fun and personality to help you learn. 
The worksheet includes:
   An explanation of the basic tools you will need for modern calligraphy
   Shinah's personal recommendations for supplies and where to find them
   Crooked Calligraphy's "Slightly Fancy" full upper-case and lower-case calligraphy alphabet
   7 pages of practice sheets to guide you through each letter 
   4 pages to practice combining the letters into words 
------------------------
PRINTING SUGGESTIONS:
This worksheet can be printed on any home printer. 
You can use tracing or bond paper over the worksheet pages to practice, or you can write directly on the printed pages themselves. 
If you are planning to write directly on the worksheet, then I recommend printing it on 28# LASERJET PAPER so your ink does not feather or bleed.

ABOUT THIS SCRUB
===================
A perfect little gift for yourself or a friend, this Wildflower Honey Sugar Scrub includes sugar and strawberry seeds for great exfoliation. 
This sugar scrub is handmade in small batches. It is a traditional, non-foaming, simple sugar scrub made mainly with sugar and moisturizing jojoba oil. It also contains potassium cocoate (an all natural potassium salt that originates from the fatty acids present in coconut oil), which provides moisturizing and light foaming.
The scrub is scented with wildflower and a touch of honey. It has a floral feel, with a warm honey undertone.
There is a full 4 oz (by weight) of this scrub in a recyclable BPA-free plastic container. 
To use, apply a small amount directly to skin, add water, scrub to exfoliate and rinse off. This product does include a preservative, so it is okay to get it wet in the shower. Just be careful, as this scrub can be slippery in the shower!
Ingredients: Sugar, jojoba oil, potassium cocoate, strawberry seeds, fragrance oil, optiphen (preservative).
This product is Paraben and MPG Free.
ABOUT ME
==========
All my products are handmade by me in very small batches in my studio in Longmont, Colorado. My soap is cold process soap, which means that I make the recipe from scratch with full control of all the ingredients. Each bar of soap cures for 4 to 6 weeks. This ensures that all the water has evaporated and leads to a harder bar of soap that will last longer.

Product name: Room Spray--8 oz.--Non GMO--Phthalate free frangrance--Gift
Description:
Berry & Birch Co has added Room Sprays to the repertoire! We are using the same non-GMO, non-toxic, phthalate free scents that you know and love! Put these attractively packaged bottles in every room and spray as needed to create a beautiful, relaxing smelling atmosphere at a moments notice. These sprays are so gentle that they can even be sprayed on fabrics and linens. 
{ SCENT CHOICES }
{ Spring & Summer Scents }
 BEAUTIFUL DAY-Fresh apple blends with dewy flower petals to create a clean, light scent that will entice the senses
BEACHWOOD-A woodsy scent expertly blended with salty, oceanic notes
TROPICAL FRUIT-A fresh citrus accent adds sweetness to this tropical delight. Lush fruity tones of sliced pineapple and ripe guava are surrounded by a medley of exotic greens to create island appeal. Clear musk underscores the fruit blend, as touches of acai berry finish to tropical blend
FLIP FLOPS-This is THE BEST Tropical Vanilla! A PERFECT Summer Scent! Tons of coconut mixed into a creamy rich vanilla!
SUMMER BOARDWALK-Yummy boardwalk smells of caramel glazed popcorn, warm taffy apples and sweet, creamy saltwater taffy. 
BERRY BELLINI-A fabulous holiday cocktail blended with juicy, sweet raspberries, red currants and tiny hints of blood orange, strawberry and peach.  Add a splash of coconut and pink sugar crystals and top if off with icy cold bubbly champagne! 
MOROCCO ORCHID-Lush Morocco orchid, sensual amber & succulent apricot capture the rich warmth of a lively marketplace and glittering desert.  Top notes of Lemon Verbena, Succulent Apricot, Desert Sand Accord, Spiced Fig.  Mid Notes of Jasmine, Marrakesh Orchid, Turmeric and bottom notes of Creamy Vanilla, Kashmir Wood, and Pink Amber.
COCONUT BLOSSOM-Sweet, thick, creamy vanilla with confectioners’ sugar sweet cherry, sweet orange citrus and the tiniest amount of yummy fresh coconut
SEA SALT BLOSSOM-Aquatic florals and sea moss mix with dewy green notes on a base of wood and musk to create an exemplary oceanic fragrance.
GREEN CLOVER & ALOE-Light, crisp green notes reminiscent of spring flowers and wild herbs. A background of light woods and warm musk complete the blend.
BLACK CEDAR WOOD & JUNIPER -A masculine blend starting with a very light citrus accord, followed by exotic florals and clove buds drying to an amber and clean woodsy base.
GEORGIA PEACH-Fresh orange sweetens this recreation of juicy, ripe peach. Green accents elevate the natural fruit sensation while lingering undertones of vanilla and musk add a velvety background for the fruit accord
POOLSIDE-A tropical mélange of blood oranges, sweet pineapples, mandarin oranges, a hint of cherry, a splash of sweet vanilla and a dash of zing will give you a taste of poolside paradise.
{Everyday Scents}
 CRANBERRY ORANGE- Delicious cranberries and juicy orange slices blend for a mouth-watering splash of sweetness.
 ROSEMARY MINT- A twist of rosemary and spearmint leaves!  This is a very minty herbal aromatic blend.
 CLEAN COTTON- A crisp linen top note leads to an innocent bouquet of fresh lavender. Sunny warmth is created with sandalwood and musk. 
 TOBACCO CARAMEL- A hint of orange adds lift to the tobacco leaf accord that characterizes this fragrance. Warm tones of oak and patchouli create dimension for the blend as a base of sweet sugary caramel balances the earthy tones. 
 HAPPY HIPPIE- Earthy patchouli is blended with refreshing lemongrass, orange oil and pine to create a clean and lovely scent. 
 COCONUT MILK LAVENDER- A beautiful and enticing blend of lavender with silky French vanilla infused with rich coconut milk and hints of musk.
 BLACKBERRY SAGE- Fresh, herbaceous notes of sage, rosemary, and mint entwine juicy, ripe blackberries. 
 SUGARED CITRUS- Raw cane sugar adds sweetness to rich mandarin orange. The aroma of vanilla    and hay add depth to the fragrance.
 REDWOOD & TONKA- Red apples, coconut milk, and red raspberries are surrounded with cedar and redwood on a base of tonka, sheer wood and vanilla beans.
 APPLE BERRY SPICE- A mouthwatering blend of autumn favorites … juicy apples, sweet berries, and warm cinnamon.
 FARMHOUSE CIDER- notes of sparkling citrus, cinnamon powder and mackintosh apple with mid notes of blush rose, clove buds and crushed greens on a base of raspberry jam, scarlet peach and sugared vanilla. 
MACINTOSH APPLE-A juicy, crisp fragrance of freshly cut mackintosh apples straight from the orchard.
AVOCADO SEA SALT-Salty marine notes blend with bright grapefruit, soft white rose, and creamy avocado to create this wonderful summer fragrance.
{Romantic Scents}
FIERCE-Refreshing masculine blend of petitgrain, cardamom, and citrus, infused jasmine and rosemary with a base of musk, oakmoss and brazilian rosewood.
TOBACCO BAYLEAF-This inviting, masculine fragrance has refreshing citrus top notes followed by exotic florals drying to a delicate background of sandalwood, cedar and warm musk.
VOLCANO-A totally delightful blend of tropical fruits and sugared oranges, lemons and limes with hints of exotic tropical florals and mountain greens
 SIMPLY SMITTEN- A blast of cherry effervescence. Fresh citrus notes of lime and orange blended with fresh cherries and berries.
 CASHMERE-Get cozy with a warm blend of cashmere cream, shimmering vanilla &  frosted clementine.  Top Notes of Cashmere Cream and Shimmering Vanilla; middle notes of Frosted Clementine and White Tea.  Bottom notes of Golden Amber and Caramel Woods.
{Bakery Scents}
  AMISH HARVEST- A rich spicy blend of cinnamon and clove is balanced with gourmand tones and butter cream and sweetened with rich vanilla to tempt the senses with this warm treat.
 CHESTNUT BROWN SUGAR- A delicious blend of caramel and rich maple combined with chestnuts in a buttery cream base.
 CINNAMON BUNS- Fresh, warm and buttery cinnamon laced yeast rolls topped with an irresistible sugary icing.
 MAPLE & CARAMEL--Rich salty butter tones blend with brown sugar to create the ultimate caramel accord for this confection. Cinnamon warms the luscious accord while maple cream adds further richness. Vanilla sugar completes the gourmand sensation.
 LEMON POUND CAKE--Decadent buttery pound cake laced with fresh grated lemon zest and   drizzled with sugary icing. Just yummy!

Product name: 100% Pure Raw Natural Honey Comb Full of Honey in Box 10 oz
Description:
Natural Honeycomb with raw honey from 2016 summer in a box approximately 10 oz (300 gr). Honey collected in northern Michigan in fields with wild flowers.  
Comb honey is a sample of nature's purest and most sweet food, having not been altered in any way, distilled from the nectar and put in the container by the bees themselves. most popular way to eat it is chew like gum. We like to scoop it into our tea, as the beeswax and honey will melt into the tea, providing natural sweetness. Each comb square is approximately 10-12 oz. 
Honey never spoils, although because it is raw and unprocessed it will granulate (thicken and crystallize) over time. 
Our bees visit wildflowers near Traverse City, Michigan. We practice chemical-free beekeeping, maintaining the health of our hives using only natural methods.

Product name: Utterly Amazing Probiotic Deodorant 2.5 oz
Description:
Note: Not all probiotic deodorants are created nor work the same. Please make sure your body products are made with high quality, organic and non GMO ingredients. You can find that promise here at Charibelle's.  This product sells all over the US with very happy customers! 
With your order you will get a 2.5 oz tube of high quality, high end Probiotic Deodorant. This deodorant is 100% NATURAL and Aluminum, Parabens, Propylene glycol, Phthalates, and Triclosan FREE, unlike most commercial deodorants. This recipe is composed of sumptuous ingredients such as Shea Butter, Cocoa Butter, Coconut Oil, Arrowroot powder and Vitamin E to nurture your skin. Strong active ingredients include Baking Soda and Probiotic Powder which many people boast about having effective powers to help improve the balance of bacteria on your skin, very similar to the way they improve the balance of bacteria in your digestive system- said in another way, you won't stink!  We use high quality ingredients including shelf stable probiotics which makes it possible to store your deodorant at room temperature instead of keeping it refrigerated. A single tube will go a long way since it takes a small amount to be effective and lasts all day.
*  Just as a tip for choosing the scent- men generally prefer the eucalyptus, bergamot or tea tree scent the best because of their deeper tones. Women seem to enjoy them all, especially lavender and lemon grass. If you have a request for a scent, please convo me and I will try to get it for you!
*The natural oils, butters and waxes used in this product have a scent of their own, the most prominent being cocoa butter and beeswax. They smell amazing on their own and blend well with essential oils.
*Want to order more than 3? Please email me and I will make you your own personal listing :)
NOTES:
*A little goes a long way! No need to "slather" the deodorant under your arms, rather patting or blotting it is the most effective way to use this. "Slathering" has the potential to discolor clothing in which we cannot be responsable for, sorry.
*This is not an antiperspirant. We believe that our bodies have their reasons for their function and to inhibit this function will disrupt the ebb and flow of the system. To sweat is normal and healthy.
*The topical use of probiotics is hitting the mainstream and is new to a lot of people. Please do your research and read testimonials on this wonderful product.
*Product is a little softer than store bought deodorant due to the natural unrefined butters and oil. It reacts to the warmth of  your skin for easy application. Remember to "pat" or "blot" your under arms instead of "slathering" it on.
*Potential irritation can occur if you are sensitive to baking soda. If you are sensitive to baking soda or think that you might be I can make your deodorant without it, please let me know.

Product name: LAVENDER | Probiotic Natural Deodorant | Organic | Vegan | Breast Health | Organic Skin Care | Green Beauty
Description:
Skin Food Probiotic Deodorant was named a product  "MUST HAVE" at a Regional Breast Cancer Awareness  Convention. 
If you are switching your beauty and personal care products and do not know where to start I strongly encourage to START HERE! Deodorant is a product that most use every single day and studies are proving that the incidence of breast cancer is on the rise. Ingredients that are present in your drug store deodorant to avoid include aluminum,parabens,Triclosan
(which is actually classified as a pesticide by the FDA), phthalates, propylene glycol and fragrance. 
When you think of the glands that are located in your armpits and knowing it takes chemicals 26 seconds to reach our blood stream....would you like to rethink directly applying these chemicals to you pits???
What you should know about Natural Deodorant....you will sweat. It is completely unnatural not to sweat.  The ingredients used in a natural deodorant will work as an odor absorbing moisturizing antimicrobial. This formula took 2 years to perfect.  Each batch is pH tested, lowering the chance of reaction and also providing you with a stable product that is extremely effective.  With a base of Coconut Oil and Shea Butter it is a soothing application and will improve the health of the underarm tissue.  The arrowroot powder absorbs moisture and provide a silky feel.
I am forgetting the best part!!! The probiotics! Balancing the bacteria and restoring your pH.  We all know we have good and bad bacteria and the benefits of probiotics. Allowing the application through a major area of absorbtion is a great way to restore balance. 
This DEO is a cream deodorant. It is recommended to be applied using your fingertips. Using a small amount of product each time gently massage into your arnpits. It will look creamy at first on the skin but then is absorbed and you are left with a layer of powders that absorb the moisture. It will only leave a residue on your clothing if you use too much or put your clothing on before the product has been absorbed. It is easily rubbed out. If you have excess deodrant left on your hands you can gently massage into your hands and it will leave them feeling soft. 
If your deodrant arrives super soft from travel I recommend to place it in the fridge to harden up a bit. Store your deodrant in a cool dry place. If traveling with your deodrant be sure to always have the lid securely in place to avoid leaking.
Keep using and you too will restore you pH and health! The primary ingredients of this deodorant have a melting temperature of about 76 degrees so it will soften in a warmer climate. You can pop this in the refrigerator to harden at any time. I prefer to keep mine in a cool dry place. My unmentionable drawer. :) I have also found that I prefer to use as a cream deodorant and apply using two fingers and lightly massaging into my arm pits! 
 
View the about page to read about the benefits and quality of oils that are used in all Products. 
You will receive a 2-2.5fl oz natural recycled twist up tube.
You can also choose to receive you deodorant in a 4 oz glass jar.

Product name: 20% sale Firm Sugar paste 12 oz jar ready to use no strips needed all natural handmade,
Description:
weight(350g) 12 oz by weight  in pet plastic jar BPA FREE 
NO-STRIP, NATURAL HAIR REMOval 
This can be used by men or women on any type of hair anywhere on the body- face, legs, armpits, bikini, back, chest, arms- anywhere!
Sugaring is less painful than conventional waxing and much safer! No burns, no chemicals - great for sensitive skin!
With Sugaring your hair will grow back finer, lighter and softer
instructions:
Before sugaring skin is cleansed of any lotions or oils and apply a light dusting of baby powder or cornstarch (see dusting powder here,  
https://www.etsy.com/listing/252375979/natural-dusting-powder-with-lavender?ref=shop_home_active_5
 
 and rub softly into skin. Remember, more isn't better. Applying too much powder will interfere with removing the hair. Powder acts as a buffer helping the paste to grasp the hair better and stick less to the skin.
take the sugaring product and roll it into a ball. Don't press too hard, just work it lightly in your hands So when you do apply it, the paste will be warmed up a bit by your body heat. keep stretching the sugar wax out with your fingers until it become opaque color 
apply sugar to hair in the OPPOSITE direction of growth firmly allowing the paste to spread as you somewhat slowly pull it. You need to use some pressure and feel like you're pressing the paste against the skin for it to stick. not just laying it on top of the hair.
The sugar paste is peeled off quickly,with fast flicking motion in the same direction as the hair growth. 
You don't want to pull your hand up, but aim for way over to the other side. You won't remove as much hair or cause breakage if you pull your straight hand up.
By removing hair in the same direction of growth also helps to avoid breaking the hair follicle either above or below the skin's surface.
This means, you'll get longer-lasting hair-free results and avoid pesky ingrown hairs
If all of the sugar doesn't come off, just put the sugar that's already in your hand with the part that is left and remove in the same fast, flicking motion.
Continuing the Process
Keep working in sections on the area that you're removing hair. If you miss some hair, you can apply it over the same area skin more than once (unlike waxing)

Description:
Natural Antiseptic Legendary Syrian Castile soap made by local Aleppian soap-maker using centuries old family recipe. 
Made with local olive and laurel bay tree fruits of Southeastern Turkey, this bar aged nine months in the open air to harden (during this time outside of the soap turns pale gold and inside remains green, creating Aleppo Soap’s trademark dual color).
The soap is so pure in its form that it only contains olive oil, laurel bay oil, sodium hydroxide and water. It has no preservatives, chemical additives or fragrances.
Added laurel bay oil (20%) makes Aleppo soap a potent antiseptic. It disinfects skin without over-drying or causing irritation. In fact, it is much safer option than the advertised antibacterial soaps which contain antibiotics and long-term use can lead to antibiotic resistant bacteria and various health problems.
Finally, longer drying time and quality of its ingredients make Aleppo Soap last much longer than other commercial soaps.  
The origin of Aleppo Soap is lost in time, however, tales about its popularity goes all the way back to famous Egyptian Queen "Cleopatra" as she used Aleppo Soap regularly to purify her skin.

Product name: Atari Punk Console Kit, Beginners DIY Electronic Project, Circuit Bent Synthesizer, Noisemaker
Description:
This Atari Punk Console kit is based on the original Stepped Tone Generator by Forest M. Mimms III. It creates great lo-fi sounds resembling those from the old style Atari games using an astable square wave oscillator.
The main features of the kit are a 9v battery connector snap, an on/off power switch, a 3.5mm jack so that it can be hooked up to other devices such as an amp, speaker or headphones, and two knobs to control the pitch and depth of the quirky raspy tones produced.  
To further customise the Atari Punk Console there are pads for soldering in your own speaker. There is also an extension strip with CV inputs for connecting the APC to other devices such as our Baby 8 Step Sequencer.
This kit is rated as easy, takes around 20-45 mins to make and is suitable for all ages. For safety it is recommended that all children are supervised during assembly!
Each kit contains clearly labelled parts for ease of use. An assembly guide with enlarged diagrams and photos with clear instructions is available to view and download on our website. If you'd prefer to receive this by email or have trouble downloading the instructions please send us a message!
A range of optional extras are available to purchase with this kit including 500mm leaded solder, a small speaker, and a connector kit (consisting of two strips of pin header sockets plus jumper wires) for connecting the APC to devices such as our Baby 8 Sequencer kit. Please use the drop down menus above to add these to your kit.
For orders of more than 10 kits please message to check availability before ordering.
Kit Includes
* PCB
* 500K Ohm Linear Potentiometer (x2)
* NE556 Dual 555 Timer IC
* 100K Resistor
* 15K Resistor
* 10K Resistor
* 1K Resistor (x2)
* 4.7K Ohm Resistor
* 10uF Electrolytic Capacitor
* 9volt (pp3) Battery Snap
* 10nF Ceramic Capacitor
* 100nF Ceramic Capacitor
* On/Off sliding switch
* 3.5mm Stereo  Jack
Battery is not included.

Product name: Real PRESSED YELLOW GINGKO Leaves - Perfect for Weddings, Events, Decorations, Art & Craft Projects, Holidays Craft, Biodegradable Decor
Description:
PRODUCT FEATURES:
• Hand picked by me in Connecticut, New England.
• Preserved using natural preservation methods with no additives in a smoke free environment.
• Contains delicate, pressed flora-fauna, handle with care.
• Avoid placing in direct sunlight to preserve colors.
• Environment friendly materials.
PRODUCT DESCRIPTION:
Each listing set consists of Real Pressed Yellow Gingko Leaves. You can choose the quantity of leaves from the drop down box during checkout. In addition, I like to see my customers happy so, I always throw in a few extras. 
These leaves are very rarely offered for sale as they have to be given a lot of special attention and care when going through the preservation process. So these are a rare find indeed.
These leaves are handpicked by me from the New England area of the Northeast and quickly pressed to retain the beautiful fall colors. The preservation process is conducted  in a pet, pesticide and smoke free environment. 
PRODUCT USE:
These dried and preserved leaves are just in time for fall weddings, Thanksgiving or Holiday events, decor, or any autumn scrapbooking art and craft project.  
Create Wedding favors, place cards, invitations or thank you notes using these pretty leaves. 
The possibilities are endless if you let your creativity loose.
Sprinkle them around tables, use them for decorating candles, making beautiful note cards or simply tape them to the window glass panes to remind yourself of Fall and its beauty.
SHIPPING & PACKAGING: 
The leaves are delicate, so we package them very carefully. We first lay them on a piece of cardboard and then use plastic wrap to hold them firmly to the cardboard and avoid internal movement. We then use bubble wrap around this package for cushioning. For additional protection during transit, we use a bubble wrap mailer.
 
Please look at our many other varieties and convo or email me if you if you have any special requests or need to order more than one. 
Plenty of stock even though listing displays only one available.

Product name: 120 grams silicone Mold Putty for making molds for cake decorating or polymer clay. Make your own silicone mold, food safe silicone
Description:
This is 120 grams (about 4 ounces) of a two-part silicone mold putty for cake decorating or polymer clay applications. It can be used for isomalt, gumpaste, or non-food materials like resin, soap, and ploymer clays. The silicone is food-grade FDA approved.
To use this you take equal parts of each color and knead them together until there are no more streaks of white and it's a consistent yellow color. Form it around the item that you're molding and let it sit to cure. 
It's about a two to three minute working time before it sets, depending on the temperature. You should have the item to be molded ready to work with, you have to work efficiently but it's very easy to work with!
This is enough to make the groups of molds that are shown in the photos. It's better to measure it with a scale, but if you have to do it by sight and use balls of it that are the same size it's pretty forgiving and you don't have to be 100% accurate for the mold to cure.

Product name: Pink Ultramarine Pigment Powder 1 Oz or 4 Oz, Pink Soap Color, Pink Mica Powder, Cosmetic Supplies,
Description:
Pink ultramarine pigment to color your cosmetics and other craft projects. It is approved for general cosmetics including skin and eye products. Matte ultramarine finish, beautiful pink to orchid shade. Use by itself or to deepen the tone of other colors. This powder has been filtered of harmful impurities. Fine particle size range from 0.3 - 1 micron. Color variations depending on the base used. This product is water & oil soluble; may speckle in melt and pour soap. To lessen the speckling, mix well and do not over use. Color will not change in products with a high pH; not light sensitive and will not migrate or bleed between layers.
You choose size of either 1 ounce weight (28 grams), approximately 4 tablespoons by dry measure or 4 ounce weight. Store at room temperature out of direct sunlight in the original zip lock bag or other air tight container. We have used in cold processed, melt and pour and liquid soaps. A little goes a long way. Used at 1/2% this is enough to color 14 pounds of soap base to a mid pink and much more if seeking a pastel shade. Use of vanilla fragrance oils will potentially change finished product after a few weeks; test all recipes in small batches for desired results.
Additional uses in bath fizzies, mineral makeup and other fun projects. Skin and eye safe; not approved for lip products.

MATERIALS
GOLD-FILLED JEWELRY:
- Under normal wearing conditions and with proper care, your gold filled jewelry should last at least 10 years.
- 14kt Gold-Filled jewelry is made by bonding a solid layer of 14kt gold on top of another metal, but this layer is 1000 - 10,000 times thicker than gold plating, resulting in a durable, long-lasting product that looks gorgeous like solid gold.
- Gold-Filled jewelry can also be worn by people with sensitive skin.
STERLING SILVER:
- We use .925 Sterling Silver, which requires polishing from time to time from oxidation. You can easily restore silver back to shine with a polishing cloth or use a polishing lotion for that extra shine.

Product name: The Riki Blazer (Women's Sizes) PDF Sewing Pattern
Description:
The Riki Blazer is a must-have for any classy wardrobe!  Designed in collaboration with Riki Prints Custom Knits, this knit pattern features two lapel options, two sleeve lengths and two hem lengths!  With flattering lines on both outer and lining fabrics, this design is completely reversible!  The perfect accessory for layering throughout all seasons!
Suggested fabric for the outer is a medium to heavyweight 2-way or 4-way stretch knit with structure and good recovery, such as ponte, Liverpool or cotton lycra.  Lining fabric can be made with a lighter weight knit.  However, any knit fabric with at least 50% stretch will work, but may not give the same results.
This listing is for a PDF sewing pattern only, not a finished garment!
This pattern is sold as an instant download after payment has cleared.
